USAGE


The model is in the N-GRAM MODEL.py file, which is the executable. At the end of this are the numeric variables to be able to change the model as required.

The different corpora are located in the Preprocess corpora file, where you can copy the corpus you want and paste it at the beginning of N-GRAM.py

To choose the back-off strategies it is the same procedure, in the file back-off strategies.py there are two different techniques and depending on which one is required, 
it is copied and pasted in N-GRAM MODEL.PY
